05:49.249 --> 06:01.361 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: Drugmaker Mylan has
been under
heavy fire for its soaring price
hikes for

06:01.394 --> 06:06.233 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
