a savings.

09:03.410 --> 09:05.879 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: Andrew Pollack, how
did this study
get so much attention?

09:05.912 --> 09:09.416 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
