09:56.129 --> 09:59.732 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Stephen Schondelmeyer, I want to
ask you a
little bit about how this could
have been

09:59.766 --> 10:01.501 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
