40:47.011 --> 40:49.547 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JACQUELINE WOODSON, Author,
"Another Brooklyn":
The basketball courts have
moved.

40:49.580 --> 40:50.782 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
