it's been renovated.

44:37.308 --> 44:42.647 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Brooklyn itself is another
Brooklyn now, gentrified,
with whites moving back in.

44:42.680 --> 44:46.884 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Woodson says she always wants to
tell the
bigger story, beyond her
characters.

44:46.918 --> 44:50.354 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JACQUELINE WOODSON: It's always
been me in
the context of the bigger world,
in the context

44:50.388 --> 44:54.859 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
