context of what
is this story trying to say, and
why is it

44:54.892 --> 45:02.266 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
trying to say it, and what does
it mean to
someone outside of this
experience?

45:02.300 --> 45:07.471 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, even as I'm creating the
characters, and
putting them on the page, and
having them

45:07.505 --> 45:09.807 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
