does it mean?

45:09.840 --> 45:14.045 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
When I put four black girls on
the page, what
is it going to mean when it goes
out into

45:14.078 --> 45:15.046 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
