45:15.079 --> 45:16.047 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
How are they going to be
represented?

45:16.080 --> 45:18.983 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
How are they going to be
digested?

45:19.016 --> 45:22.720 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
So -- and what is my
responsibility in all
of that?

45:22.753 --> 45:26.057 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
